data.PS: The following links are only valid for module list maintainers:
data.rationale:
Provides an Application Header Block 2 for building a SWIFT
    message.

    The class may be used directly by any application, but it's built
    primarily to support the planned SWIFT::Factory::MTnnn family of
    classes.
